@startuml StudentJoinMeeting-Sequence
!theme plain
scale 0.75
skinparam dpi 150
title Sequence Diagram: Siswa Join Kelas Online (Jitsi Meets)

actor "Siswa" as Siswa
control ":OnlineMeetingController" as Controller <<control>>
entity ":OnlineMeeting" as Meeting <<entity>>
entity ":Classroom" as Classroom <<entity>>
control ":JitsiService" as Jitsi <<control>>
database ":Database" as DB

== View Available Meetings ==
Siswa -> Controller: Lihat Kelas Online
activate Controller

Controller -> Classroom: Ambil Kelas Siswa
activate Classroom
Classroom -> DB: Retrieve
activate DB
DB --> Classroom: Data
deactivate DB
Classroom --> Controller: Data Kelas
deactivate Classroom

Controller -> Meeting: Ambil Active Meetings
activate Meeting
Meeting -> DB: Retrieve with Filter
activate DB
DB --> Meeting: Data
deactivate DB
Meeting --> Controller: List Meetings
deactivate Meeting

Controller --> Siswa: Tampilkan Daftar Meeting
deactivate Controller

== Join Meeting ==
Siswa -> Controller: Klik Join Meeting
activate Controller

Controller -> Meeting: Cari Meeting
activate Meeting
Meeting -> DB: Retrieve
activate DB
DB --> Meeting: Data
deactivate DB
Meeting --> Controller: Data Meeting
deactivate Meeting

alt Meeting Tidak Aktif
  Controller --> Siswa: Error: Meeting Belum/Sudah Selesai
else Meeting Aktif
  
  Controller -> Jitsi: Generate Join URL
  activate Jitsi
  Jitsi --> Controller: Jitsi URL for Student
  deactivate Jitsi
  
  Controller --> Siswa: Redirect ke Jitsi Room
end

deactivate Controller

@enduml
